Description: Supplementary compatibility updates for factoextra (Kassambara & Mundt,
    2020). Modern R ecosystem support (ggplot2 >= 4.0.0, ggpubrplus >= 0.9.0,
    FactoMineR >= 2.13, R >= 4.1.0) - to be cited with the original package.
    Provides easy-to-use functions to extract and visualize
    the output of multivariate data analyses, including 'PCA' (Principal Component
    Analysis), 'CA' (Correspondence Analysis), 'MCA' (Multiple Correspondence Analysis),
    'FAMD' (Factor Analysis of Mixed Data), 'MFA' (Multiple Factor Analysis) and
    'HMFA' (Hierarchical Multiple Factor Analysis) functions from different R packages.
    It contains also functions for simplifying some clustering analysis steps and
    provides 'ggplot2'-based elegant data visualization.
